
@startuml
actor User
participant Frontend
participant "Flask API" as API
participant "APIFree LLM" as LLM
participant "Image Generation API" as ImageAPI
participant "Generated Outputs" as Outputs
User -> Frontend: Enter profile data
Frontend -> API: Submit generation request
API -> LLM: Send profile and prompt templates
LLM --> API: Return website content
API -> ImageAPI: Send visual generation prompt
ImageAPI --> API: Return generated image
API -> Outputs: Save HTML, API, docs, UML
Outputs --> API: Confirm files created
API --> Frontend: Return package
Frontend --> User: Display/download outputs
@enduml
